name: Depot Habbatussauda
address: Depot habbatussauda, timur samping balai banjar, Pas samping balai banjar banyuning timut, Jl. Setia Budi No.76, Banyuning, Kec. Buleleng, Kabupaten Buleleng, Bali, Indonesia
review 1:
Love the food, great taste and quality.

An important note, this is Indonesian take on Biryani or Kabsa or kebabs. Although they are very tasty, they are in no way close to being authentic. The main reason being the inability to obtain spices and ingredients in Indonesia. But a solid 10/10 for effort and presentation.

So if you're looking for a change or want to try something different out of the ordinary local food, this is the best one to try. Plus the prices are almost the same as you'd pay at a local food stall.
